<div class="min-h-screen bg-neutral-950 text-neutral-200 font-sans selection:bg-rose-500/30">
  <Layouts.flash_group flash={@flash} />
  
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden pt-16 pb-32 lg:pt-32">
    <!-- Decorative background elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <div class="absolute -top-[10%] -left-[10%] w-[120%] h-[120%] bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjgiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSI4IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjgiIGZpbGw9IiNmZmYiIGZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eT0iMC4wMiIvPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEiIGZpbGw9IiNmZmYiIGZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eT0iMC4xIi8+PC9zdmc+')] opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -m-32 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-rose-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -m-32 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/50 shadow-sm backdrop-blur">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-neutral-100" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight text-neutral-100">AiProviders Mock API</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
          Local, deterministic <br/><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-rose-400 to-indigo-400">OpenAI mocks.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-400 mb-10">
          This service provides a lightweight, deterministic simulation of the OpenAI API. It allows you to develop and test OpenAI integrations locally without authenticating against or paying for the real service.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mb-16">
          <a href="https://api.openai.test:4900/v1/models" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-950 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-200">
            View Models
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 10a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h10.638L10.23 5.29a.75.75 0 111.04-1.08l5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 010 1.08l-5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 11-1.04-1.08l4.158-3.96H3.75A.75.75 0 013 10z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#endpoints" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-900/50 backdrop-blur px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-300 transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-800 hover:text-white">
            See Endpoints
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 lg:px-8 pb-32 pt-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 border-t border-neutral-800/60 pt-12">
      <div>
        <h3 id="endpoints" class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205l3 1m1.5.5l-1.5-.5M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636l10.5-3.819" />
          </svg>
          Available API Endpoints
        </h3>
        <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-6 font-mono bg-neutral-900/50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 inline-block">
          Base URL: <span class="text-neutral-200">https://api.openai.test:4900</span>
        </div>
        
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800/80 bg-neutral-900/30 p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-800/50 hover:border-neutral-700">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm text-rose-400 mb-1 font-medium">GET /v1/models</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">List all available mock chat and embedding models.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800/80 bg-neutral-900/30 p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-800/50 hover:border-neutral-700">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm text-indigo-400 mb-1 font-medium">POST /v1/chat/completions</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Generate deterministic chat completion responses based on prompts.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800/80 bg-neutral-900/30 p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-800/50 hover:border-neutral-700">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm text-emerald-400 mb-1 font-medium">POST /v1/embeddings</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Create mock embedding vectors from string or array inputs.</div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="sticky top-12">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-rose-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.25 9.75L16.5 12l-2.25 2.25m-4.5 0L7.5 12l2.25-2.25M6 20.25h12A2.25 2.25 0 0020.25 18V6A2.25 2.25 0 0018 3.75H6A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 6v12A2.25 2.25 0 006 20.25z" />
            </svg>
            Quick Start with Bruno
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-4">
            The easiest way to interact with the mock endpoints is through the provided 
            <strong class="text-neutral-200 font-semibold">Bruno API collection</strong>.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-neutral-900/80 rounded-xl p-5 border border-neutral-800 shadow-inner relative overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-800/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-4 space-y-4 m-0 text-sm text-neutral-400 relative z-10">
              <li>Open the <code class="text-rose-400 bg-rose-400/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-xs">bruno/ai-providers-mock/</code> directory in the Bruno app.</li>
              <li>Select the <code class="text-neutral-200 bg-neutral-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-xs">local</code> environment. The base URL will point to <code class="text-neutral-200 bg-neutral-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-xs">api.openai.test:4900</code>.</li>
              <li>Open any request (like <code class="text-neutral-200 bg-neutral-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-xs">03-chat-completions.bru</code>) and click <strong class="text-white">Send</strong>.</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 text-sm text-orange-200">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-orange-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a.75.75 0 000 1.5h.253a.25.25 0 01.244.304l-.459 2.066A1.75 1.75 0 0010.747 15H11a.75.75 0 000-1.5h-.253a.25.25 0 01-.244-.304l.459-2.066A1.75 1.75 0 009.253 9H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <p>Authentication is intentionally bypassed in this mock application to keep test client configuration minimal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>